{"word":"G4927 - συνομορέω - synomoréō - soon-om-or-eh'-o - Join hard","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνομορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synomoréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-om-or-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Join hard</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அடுத்ததாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to border on, be contiguous to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and a derivative of a compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G3674 - ὁμοῦ - homoû - hom-oo'/3674\">G3674</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G3725 - ὅριον - hórion - hor'-ee-on/3725\">G3725</a>; to <i>border together</i>, that is, <i>adjoin:</i> - join hard.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}